---
title: Creamy Chicken and Mushroom Filo Pie with Carrots
description: This Creamy Chicken and Mushroom Filo Pie with Carrots brings crisp, crunchy pastry together with a rich filling. A tasty dish to cook on chilly winter evenings this season.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF220905_R05_W44_UK_R10512-2_KB_Main_low-fb348460.jpg
